Fernandes told talkSPORT: 'Yes, we can (afford not to go up). I'm an accountant by background - although I may not seem it!

'We've told the fans, whether we go up or we don't, we're here for the long term.

'We know what culture we want at the club and we will continue the journey whether we're in the Championship or the Premier League.

'We are a much smarter, much wiser group of people than we were two years ago.'

